@startuml CreateCourses
|Admin|
start
:1. Open course creation form;
:2. Fill in course details (title, description, code);
:3. Submit form;
|CourseDashboard|
:4. Validate course data;
|CourseController|
:5. Check if course already exists;
:6. Create new course in backend;
|Database|
:7. Save course record;
|CourseController|
:8. Return success;
|CourseDashboard|
:9. Display confirmation;
:10. Update course list;
stop
@enduml
